// Check if unlockAchievement is already defined as a function if (typeof unlockAchievement !== 'function') { // Store achievements that have already been unlocked window.unlockedAchievements = new Set(); // Define the unlockAchievement function window.unlockAchievement = function(achievementName) { // Check if this achievement has already been unlocked if (!window.unlockedAchievements.has(achievementName)) { // Show the achievement popup alert("Unlocked Achievement: " + achievementName); // Add this achievement to the set to mark it as unlocked window.unlockedAchievements.add(achievementName); } else { // Optional: Do something if the achievement is already unlocked console.log("Achievement '" + achievementName + "' has already been unlocked."); } }; } // Example usage changeCandidateMargins = (candidate, boost) => { for (i in e.candidate_state_multiplier_json) { if (e.candidate_state_multiplier_json[i].fields.candidate != candidate) { continue; } let marg = e.candidate_state_multiplier_json[i].fields.state_multiplier let maxPk = e.candidate_state_multiplier_json[e.candidate_state_multiplier_json.length-1].pk e.candidate_state_multiplier_json[i] = { "model":"campaign_trail.candidate_state_multiplier", "pk":maxPk + 1, "fields": { "candidate": candidate, "state": e.candidate_state_multiplier_json[i].fields.state, "state_multiplier": marg + boost } } } return true; } const recommendedReading = `

2024: Democracy’s Martyrdom

Credits

Rubix–Lead Writer and Coder

Gloryofrome–Co-Writer and Advisor

Ohas–Effects Coder

Oohweeooh–Assistant Coder and Writer

Outfox–Assistant Coder and Writer

Emmy the Gremlin–Assistant FoPo Writer and Style Designer

Pedro–Assistant FoPo Writer and Style Designer

Onkel Danny–Assistant Coder

Bobby–Assistant FoPo Writer

Hamcrackers–Style Designer

Script–Banner Designer(Democrats Vs Trump)

El Prez–Banner Designer(Democratic Infinity)

Director’s Commentary

Hey!

This mod has been a lot–and taken a lot from me.

For quite a while, I thought I’d have more to say on this–but we’re within 12 hours of release as I write this, and I’m frankly very drained at the moment. Democracy’s Martyrdom as the idea first came to me in late February, and now, in early October, we’ve made it. The scores of questions and errors and CYOA and everything I learned is going to stay with me for a while, as are the amount of people who have expressed such kindness and an eagerness to play the finished product. I truly do hope I live up to expectations.

Anywho–onto talking about the mod. It’s been a lot, and I bet there will be a contingent of disappointed people here. Yes, it’s a fakeout. Yes, it’s not really an 8 candidate mod like many were expecting—though there are 8 different nominees who can all have questions where they are the playable ones. Given the saturation of 2024 mods, I don’t expect this to be too sorely felt as a missed opportunity.

I’m so incredibly grateful to each and every person who worked on this mod–I expected it to just be me bugging Rome about it for a few months and I’d release it in early July, but now it’s a huge staff team mod with a lot of people working on it, and it’s been delayed 2 official times Either way, we’re here now.

Thank you so much, everyone. Also I do not hate iranians.

Special Thanks

Hamcrackers, as always, for being one of the most wonderful people I know.

A certain IRL friend of mine who I’m grateful to for being so supportive.

Lawrence Eagleburger, for having that name and inspiring this whole mod.

- Rubix, 10/03/2024
